## 2. SOLID Principle Review

| Principle | Review Results |
| :--- | :--- |
| **SRP (Single Responsibility)** | [Bridge](file:///c:/Users/1-16/Desktop/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/src/edge_device/bridge.h#48-49) class is now organized into specialized loops ([sensorLoop](file:///c:/Users/1-16/Desktop/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/src/edge_device/bridge.cpp#161-236), [deviceInfoLoop](file:///c:/Users/1-16/Desktop/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/src/edge_device/bridge.cpp#128-161), [readerLoop](file:///c:/Users/1-16/Desktop/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/src/edge_device/bridge.cpp#237-253)), each with a distinct responsibility. |
| **OCP (Open/Closed)** | New sensors or system metrics can be added with minimal impact on the core communication logic. |
| **LSP (Liskov Substitution)** | [SystemResourceMonitor](file:///c:/Users/1-16/Desktop/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/src/system/SystemResourceMonitor.h#15-32) correctly implements the [IResourceMonitor](file:///c:/Users/1-16/Desktop/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/src/system/IResourceMonitor.h#27-34) interface, allowing for alternative monitor implementations if needed. |
| **ISP (Interface Segregation)** | Using specialized packet types (`AVAILABLE` vs `META`) ensures the server only processes the specific data it needs. |
| **DIP (Dependency Inversion)** | The bridge logic depends on the [IResourceMonitor](file:///c:/Users/1-16/Desktop/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/src/system/IResourceMonitor.h#27-34) abstraction, enabling easier testing and modularity. |

