## 4. Verification Results

- [x] **System Metrics**: `AVAILABLE` packets now contain real RPi SoC temperature and usage statistics, sent every 5 seconds.
- [x] **Sensor Data**: `META` packets correctly package the environmental `light` sensor data alongside others.
- [x] **Network Stability**: [CommandServer](file:///c:/Users/1-16/Desktop/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/SubCameraApp_refactory_260306_queue_sensor%20communicate_ai%20ingredient/src/network/CommandServer.cpp#10-11) logs show clean, synchronized packet reception at the binary level.
- [x] **Resource Protection**: Mutex-guarded loops prevent UART contention during simultaneous status/motor commands.

